Hack
====

What is this?
-------------

This repository contains your Hack toolchain implementation:

* A Hack Assembler in C
* A Hack Virtual Machine Translator in C
* A Hack Compiler in Python

The project currently builds two tools:

* Assembler/Assembler
* VirtualMachine/VMTranslator


Building
--------

To build everything:

	make all

To remove generated binaries:

	make clean


Tool Usage
----------

Assembler:

	./Assembler/Assembler path/to/file.asm

VM Translator:

	./VirtualMachine/VMTranslator path/to/file.vm

Compiler:

    python3 Compiler/JackCompiler.py path/to/file.jack


Project Layout
--------------

Assembler/
	Assembler.c      - Entry point for the assembler
	Parser.c/.h      - Parses Hack assembly commands
	Code.c/.h        - Converts mnemonics to binary fields
	SymbolTable.c/.h - Symbol table management

VirtualMachine/
	VMTranslator.c   - Entry point for the VM translator
	Parser.c/.h      - Parses VM commands
	CodeWriter.c/.h  - Emits Hack assembly output

Compiler/
	Python compiler implementation